name: All Frogs Go To Heaven #001
description: It was dawning when this little frog's light finally extingueshed. The air was soft, not a breeze in sight. It doesn't remember how, it only knows it was painless. Saturated with emotion, it struggled, then struggled no more. Its surroundings faded, then started reshaping into forms of other frogs it met before but never again. Until now.
